```mermaid
flowchart TB
  clickExample[点击 Example / 首次进入]
  clickExample --> loggedIn{已登录?}
  loggedIn -->|否| staticLoad[加载静态 example.mmd]
  loggedIn -->|是| tryLoad["GET /api/load?folder=示例&id=欢迎"]
  tryLoad --> exists{存在?}
  exists -->|是| openExisting[打开已有文件]
  exists -->|否| seedSave["POST /api/save 写入示例内容"]
  seedSave --> openNew[打开新文件]
``